node.text: Sam, Golden Retriever (16 y/o), Upper West Side, New York, NY • We’ve partnered with @thefarmersdog to tell the story of Sam, a senior rescue dog who’s living a long, fulfilling and healthy life. The Farmer’s Dog is helping senior dogs in shelters find homes in time for the holidays – follow the link at the end of the video to see adoptable seniors in shelters all across the country so hopefully you can find a Sam, too.

node.text: Announcing our exciting new collaboration with @bffsandbabes! It’s summertime, it’s hot, the dogs are swimming, and YOU are in the mood for a cold beverage while wearing your tie-dye tee (we know we are). We designed this extra-fun version of our classic Dogist tee – each shirt was individually tie-dyed by hand by the awesome people at @BFFSandBabes. This is a limited edition release, so… you know the deal. Get them while they’re here! Shop now at the link in bio.
